val.  The sectors will each have a mayor who will be in charge of most of the sector affairs and mayors will be elected by their own sectors and can serve for one year.'; document.getElementById('title').innerHTML='Sectors'"  target="" /><area shape="rect" alt="" title="general" coords="75,338,665,464" href="" onMouseOver="document.getElementById('desc').innerHTML='The general population will be able to directly vote on all proposed laws and will be able to propose laws to the supreme representatives through their sectors.  The general population will have more of a say than people in systems such as those of the United States because of their direct connection to all proposed laws.  Elections will be based on popular vote rather than the electoral vote system.'; document.getElementById('title').innerHTML='General Population'"  target="" /></map>
